## If All Three Pass — Run the Test Suite

```bash
python -m pytest tests/integration/test_e2e_phase1.py -v -s
```

The `-s` flag is important — it lets stdout from the nodes (including the `_validate_test_cases` warnings) print live so you can watch the pipeline progress in real time.

